{"tid":2402670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在港緬甸人組織：不承認軍人政權　譴責任何支持軍政府的國家","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T18:34:05.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3132961afc5c61ae262832648a9aca1f5992c80","tid":2402670,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3416232048515746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoseph.lo.1840%2Fposts%2F3416232048515746&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=51e88d68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3416232048515746</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fhu1oxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhu1oxS.jpg&h=5d06a981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Joseph Lo<br />\n<br />\n【🇲🇲緬甸戰線｜在港緬甸人組織：不承認軍人政權 譴責任何支持軍政府的國家 港人團體聲援】<br />\n<br />\n緬甸抗爭持續，有在港緬甸人組織剛發表聲明，聲援在緬甸抗爭的手足，批評軍政府發動政變，濫捕昂山素姬、國會議員、政客、僧人、社運人士，要求軍政府立即放人。相關聲明同時獲得羅冠聰、民陣等多個公民團體或個人支持。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調，不會承認軍政府政權，並譴責所有以任何形式，包括金錢、技術、物資或意識形態上支持或協助緬甸非法政權的國家、組織或個人。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會早前討論是否譴責緬甸軍方政變，惟因中俄阻撓，一度拖延譴責。聯合國人權理事會周五將召開特別會議，討論緬甸軍方政變奪權後的局勢，並準備表決一份與緬甸局勢相關的決議案。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸全國示威已經進入第四日，《路透社》指出緬甸抗爭者如何受到香港及泰國手足啟發，尤其是年青一代在抗爭中的角色。另外，當局連用用水砲驅趕人民，甚至發現有實彈，令當地抗爭者同樣面對警暴問題。聯合國駐緬甸代表亦批評當局使用不合比例的武力，令示威者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n明顯地，緬甸抗爭將會繼續發酵，紐西蘭今日剛公布對緬甸軍隊高層實制個人制裁，禁止他們入境，並終止與緬甸的高層對話，相信其他國家日後會陸續有跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TMclaughlin3/status/1359113661235666957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTMclaughlin3%2Fstatus%2F1359113661235666957&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=a2fcd94b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTMclaughlin3%2Fstatus%2F1359113661235666957&h=07273327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TMclaughlin3/status/1359113661235666957</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1359117345260773381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1359117345260773381&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=c80b6dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1359117345260773381&h=cdeede69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1359117345260773381</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KenRoth/status/1359134432196780036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKenRoth%2Fstatus%2F1359134432196780036&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=7a6597dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKenRoth%2Fstatus%2F1359134432196780036&h=bcc7d10a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/KenRoth/status/1359134432196780036</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1359087274261110789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1359087274261110789&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=da3c32fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1359087274261110789&h=6e7ca0b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1359087274261110789</a>"},{"pid":"0a7552f066acbb437a9d012126915e360d79d721","tid":2402670,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"佢哋要唔要物資？<br />\n點寄？<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">雖然好似好左膠 淨係識捐嘢</span>"}]}